{"tid":2149242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴基斯坦連三日大雨洪災 超過60人死多人傷","createTime":"2020-08-10T09:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T03:35:29.000Z","uid":295230,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce2714136fb30451de60072c739b0eea61790d6","tid":2149242,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T09:54:27.000Z","msg":"巴基斯坦廣泛地區過去三天遭暴雨侵襲, 沖毀四座橋樑, 導致300多幢房屋損毀, 幾百個村莊道路中斷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s5uREk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs5uREk5.jpg&h=2e5560ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《美聯社》報導，據巴基斯坦國家災難管理局表示，水災在過去3天裡造成49人罹難，分別為西北的開伯爾-普什圖省（Khyber Pakhtunkhwa）19人、南部信德省12人、旁遮普省（Punjab）8人和北部吉爾吉特-巴爾蒂斯坦地區（Gligit Baltistan）10人。<br />\n<br />\n暴雨也侵襲了西南部巴魯支斯坦省（Baluchistan），據當地媒體報導，至少八人因強降雨及山洪暴發而喪命。<br />\n<br />\n大雨從上週持續到今日（9日），洪水甚至氾濫到東部城市拉哈爾（Lahore），信德省省會克拉嗤（Karachi）也發生嚴重淹水，污水淹沒了當地大部分街道，促使總理伊姆蘭（Imran Khan）下令軍隊乘船疏散民眾。"},{"pid":"63c9d4b81589ae957b0b5259b4443e019b8ffc1e","tid":2149242,"uid":50740,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"叫支那起個水霸幫你地擋災囉"},{"pid":"8a2380136d7a7105065bbd9ec8cf121e11cbb6e7","tid":2149242,"uid":91771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"連巴鐵都出埋事<br />\n支那班𡃁呢排多災多難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a53fed694ca616dbd6e3f5a716ea33e2dba941","tid":2149242,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:09:42.000Z","msg":"阿拉花瓜柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70a0d5c5f624f86bce4f660853d793134f684bc","tid":2149242,"uid":45660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:14:52.000Z","msg":"可以叫雜種施捨幾個錢<br />\n又可以消滅低端人口<br />\n諗起都爽"},{"pid":"e49704dfc96f1b2f2ad5f4bfc18e76ad836e7af0","tid":